  "reference_number": "IRN0238",
  "remarks": "\nHossein Pourfarzaneh is an involved person within the meaning of the Iran (Sanctions) Regulations 2023 on the basis of the following ground: Hossein Pourfarzaneh is or has been involved in hostile activity by the Government of Iran, namely by working as a manager of an entity carrying on business in the Iranian defence sector, in his role as Chief Engineer of Farzanegan Propulsion Systems Design Bureau (FPSDB).\n",
